.
\begin_inset Newpage pagebreak
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Demostracion
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
En efecto 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{j}=\left(0v_{1}+\ldots+1v_{j}+\ldots+0v_{n}\right)\in\left\langle \left\{ v_{1},v_{2},\ldots,v_{n}\right\} \right\rangle $
