Sean 
\begin_inset Formula $u,w\in\left\langle \left\{ v_{1},v_{2},\ldots,v_{n}\right\} \right\rangle $
\end_inset

 luego 
\begin_inset Formula $u=\alpha_{1}v_{1}+\ldots+\alpha_{n}v_{n}$
\end_inset

