 un polinomio tal que 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{\ensuremath{P\left(T\right)=0}}$
\end_inset

 y 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{\ensuremath{U_{i}=\mathcal{N}\left(T-\alpha_{i}I\right)^{m_{i}}}}$
\end_inset

 entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

 es la suma directa de los subespacios 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{1},\ldots,U_{r}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

